{"tid":1933480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌晒你地老母！","createTime":"2020-03-19T10:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T10:08:58.000Z","uid":309023,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fe5b25ae62ea41236f563d75a1b9420077870fb4","tid":1933480,"uid":309023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:08:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我屌哂你哋老母！</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地自己睇吓個熱門似咩樣？<br />\n係咪光復左香港 五大訴求達到左啦？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">睇唔到d 手足 一個一個比人係天台掟落街既<br />\n睇唔到d 藍屍 十八區搞街站 派口罩呃簽名 支持23條既<br />\n睇唔到d 黑警晚晚咬人大搜捕既<br />\n睇唔到林奠 日日落區 行cat walk 既<br />\n睇唔到國際戰線著晒火既<br />\n睇唔到支共日日做大外宣 話美國輸入病毒去中國既？</span><br />\n如果呢個post上唔到熱門 冇哂行動post 我正式宣布呢個運動真係玩完 連登已死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連我個淺藍老母都問啲暴徒係咪搞完事 <br />\n<br />\n外國戰線著撚哂火咁大粒核彈都冇人理既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n應承我 唔好當手足係condom<br />\n我哋要揸住佢個春袋 呢粒核彈會令到中共好驚 手足就嚟贏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n千祈唔可以中五毛 分化撚 PR公司嘅計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推走熱門啲行動Post 唔係既話我哋真係會就嚟輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後我都唔講咁多<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命 五大訴求 缺一不可 煲底見</span></span>！ <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}